expression = re.compile(rfc._COOKIE_OCTET_REGEX)
unallowed_values = ['\x00', '\x01', '\x02', '\x03', '\x04', '\x06', '\x07',
    '\x08', '\t', '\n', '\t', '\x0c', '\r', '\x0e', '\x0f', '\x10', '\x11',
    '\x12', '\x13', '\x14', '\x15', '\x16', '\x17', '\x18', '\x19', '\x1a',
    '\x1b', '\x1c', '\x1d', '\x1e', '\x1f', ' ', '"', ',', ';', '\\', '\x7f']
for unallowed_value in unallowed_values:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(unallowed_value)), msg=
        "Unallowed Octedt '{u}' matched by regex".format(u=unallowed_value))
